Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 帮我拿酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来伸出手不就拿到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就不用酱油了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这紧张兮兮的气氛是怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷不知道你在那边发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过难得大家一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能开心一点嘛 怎么样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 好冷哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子她妈 她到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看 茶叶梗立起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远隔万里而相通的二人之心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像已经好久没有来学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由加 绘理 步美 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你怎么还这么悠闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你得了economy class症候群请假的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}economy class症候群：实际上不存在这种疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么乱七八糟的症候群啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷又学会新的病名了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩是一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段时间总是缠着北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学好像也不是很讨厌她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么办？这不是好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着不管可是会被抢走的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方才一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮肤又这么光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是北条同学那样的男生最喜欢的类型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我又没在跟北条同学交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然另外有男朋友对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能会表现得这么平静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我光是想起他就一肚子火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要快点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在怀疑我什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你刚才一直是那样看我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要冲我发脾气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是你自己有那种奇怪的误会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想看到你这张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你去哪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去钢牙那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都只是一口古井而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里跟戈薇的国家连在一起的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是能通过古井的只有戈薇和犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只有犬夜叉能去接戈薇回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只没大脑的笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不知道在赌什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有人在背后说我坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 有人说你坏话也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的确干了那么多蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 老太婆 你说我做了什么蠢事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋就是笨蛋 无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要找出四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的灵力是不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却搞不清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还把她给气回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是她自己擅自跑回去的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说什么“我要回家了 笨蛋”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你学戈薇一点都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情有什么所谓嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 请大家排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 姑娘的手相不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以后会很长寿而且子孙满堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人 是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意为我生个孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人你好讨厌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人刚才也跟我说了一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要看到美女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就忍不住想要对方为我生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这么看来似乎有点苗头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不知道我能不能一次满足你们二位呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人好讨厌哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是老头子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们现在怎么急也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非犬夜叉能够好好冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我们几个根本是无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉笨得无可救药了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上他的脾气又臭又硬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看是没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后最好不要靠近枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想想犬夜叉的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是发现有人在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他想去接戈薇小姐也去不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那家伙与表面相反
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心也有很可爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不可貌相啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们眼前就有个最好的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 没人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇那家伙 我还是无法原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对 要让她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这次你逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在跟什么样的男生交往啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个小气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野蛮任性又暴躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是个超～级醋坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果爱吃醋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就表示他很喜欢戈薇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 原来很顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会更有趣点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人对戈薇很专情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样的话我也没话说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙没办法忘记以前喜欢过的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都犹豫不决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛 仔细想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉明明是喜欢桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要因为我吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇受到了很猛烈的追求对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人还想杀了接近我的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你为什么要跟那种人交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须跟他分手 绝对不能再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是野蛮又任性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还脚踏两条船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是他也有优点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人很温柔 而且很强大很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是喜欢他吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢…？我喜欢犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇一定是喜欢他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 她不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…充满了戈薇的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是戈薇姐姐的弟弟 叫草太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来玩的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你们没有吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐看上去心情很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在生气啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人真爱计较
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么突然觉得好累…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 狗狗哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要告诉戈薇我到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是男人之间的约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人之间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么随便进别人的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个…这是男人之间的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时犬夜叉这么辛苦跑来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却站在钢牙那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…是我不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会向她道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙到底去干什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个让人操心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你自己说不准我们靠近枯井的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情就是要观看过程才好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到学校里来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病已经好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们最近都没时间好好谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这周的周末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该回去比较好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你周六没空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会去吧 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 周六见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们干嘛擅自帮我决定嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像北条同学这样正常的男人才适合戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跟那个醋坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又花心 还有暴力倾向的男生交往下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的将来会很悲惨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在说犬夜叉吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 你一定要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉还在生气吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本来就很顽固的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想看到你那张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊…现在回去的话可能又要吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为姐姐看上去心情很不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…不要突然冒出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赶紧去接她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那岂不是好像是我错了一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是你不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在怀疑戈薇是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还说要决斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是那种时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙受伤了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇确实保护了钢牙让他逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道钢牙是犬夜叉的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且戈薇还不计较自己被他劫持并遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 明明最受钢牙欺负的是戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她还要帮钢牙啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇说不定真的喜欢上了钢牙对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要问我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要劝人家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先想好一套说词再来行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在给我滚吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 犬夜叉 刚才是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死人了 你真的是很烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过不去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就绝对不会去接她！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 你先听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这种麻烦的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找人生经验丰富的枫姥姥商量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是最好的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心 我不会说出你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就假装是要问我朋友的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是可以稍微听你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 只…只是稍微哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢 我是帮我一个狗狗朋友来找你商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 你那个狗朋友怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个狗狗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢上一只猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了一匹野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对猫咪一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗与野狼每次见面都会打架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野狼 从狗狗身边抢走了猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是仇恨野狼的妖怪出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野狼受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后赶来救猫咪的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使消灭了妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗想把受伤的野狼也一并收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪却保护了野狼 让他逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪只是保护了受伤的野狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗却怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪是不是喜欢上那只野狼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后猫咪就生气地回到了自己的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 事情大概就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让狗狗和猫咪和好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先狗要承认自己错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你激动什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是在说七宝的狗朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 猫咪可能等狗狗去接她等得都不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这两个人都误会了对方所以无法和好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要让两个人见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是解决问题最快捷的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你还要在这边待多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 我不能在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在学业繁忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能总是跑去战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就总是跑去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为犬夜叉会来带我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能已经不会来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会知道那种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是姐姐一直在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不来的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直在生气…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一早再起来念书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在根本集中不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被子好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边根本就睡不舒服啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉会替我值夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在…他在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦话？她梦到我了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这臭丫头到底在做什么梦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹钟不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…是犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以周六不能陪你去看电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别介意我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那个一年级的女孩子去看电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺喜欢北条同学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真傻 原来你是在意那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不打算跟别的女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我有点高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮原来因为我在吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我下次再约你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学真坚强…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也能像那样自信满满的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈…戈薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正犬夜叉不会道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我稍微向他低头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在生气对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到犬夜叉会这么老实地向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 真的不生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你说是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为你弄坏了这个闹钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然你以为还有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉其实是在反省的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还去了你那边两次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从戈薇走了以后 他就一直在叹气…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了两次？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们不要多嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道我去那边了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 既然已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就先老实道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰唆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我们吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不干呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是担心你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要你们多管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我必须要道歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真激动啊 因为他高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇回来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是我的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样…风穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事就吸我进去！
